title: Mon Post Show – The Investigative Morning Corny…After Dark! (03-21-22)

description:
Bobby starts by talking to Listener Gary who also applied to be on CBS’s Superfan because he’s been to over 75 Little Big Town concerts. We give our percentage of whether Morgan will make it on the show. Amy does an Investigative Morning Corny After Dark. Morgan2 got flipped off at a Morgan Wallen concert.
